{"tid":885482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有公屋你住唔住","createTime":"2018-11-01T10:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T08:05:25.000Z","uid":166622,"like":50,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"17a0696d7a489d5502c6e626bb685c25b663d8af","tid":885482,"uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:52:02.000Z","msg":"人生難題<br />\n依定嗰個都想要公屋，但向地鐵同車聲<br />\n樓層唔高，又有可能多老鼠<br />\n有無人會照要？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =梗係要啦 公屋仔無敵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 有噪音不了"},{"pid":"2cd055c12ca594f8e3b3e0c8543e38941711a97a","tid":885482,"uid":27568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T12:52:09.000Z","msg":"向地鐵即係近地鐵站啦<br />\n緊係狗衝<br />\n<br />\n好似我咁<br />\n住遠離地鐵要轉巴士<br />\n收工時間仲要打晒蛇餅<br />\n你就知近地鐵幾咁好<br />\n新樓空氣好清靜都唔及交通方便呀<br />\n除非你唔使返工返學同買野啦"},{"pid":"5f3eb0bdec7a3d25662d84e3e2ccb9ea87daa59d","tid":885482,"uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cd055c12ca594f8e3b3e0c8543e38941711a97a","tid":885482,"uid":27568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T12:52:09.000Z","msg":"向地鐵即係近地鐵站啦<br />\n緊係狗衝<br />\n<br />\n好似我咁<br />\n住遠離地鐵要轉巴士<br />\n收工時間仲要打晒蛇餅<br />\n你就知近地鐵幾咁好<br />\n新樓空氣好清靜都唔及交通方便呀<br />\n除非你唔使返工返學同買野啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"的確係近地鐵，行過去十分鐘，返工又近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a818664f5c6b8af3c7a1218ba39bbc83b6e2ab","tid":885482,"uid":27568,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5f3eb0bdec7a3d25662d84e3e2ccb9ea87daa59d","tid":885482,"uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cd055c12ca594f8e3b3e0c8543e38941711a97a","tid":885482,"uid":27568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T12:52:09.000Z","msg":"向地鐵即係近地鐵站啦<br />\n緊係狗衝<br />\n<br />\n好似我咁<br />\n住遠離地鐵要轉巴士<br />\n收工時間仲要